title: FULL SHOW: We Open The Phone Lines About Boosie Comments On Relationships and Social Media, We Speak On The Beef Between Latto And Nicki Minaj & More
itunes:title: FULL SHOW: We Open The Phone Lines About Boosie Comments On Relationships and Social Media, We Speak On The Beef Between Latto And Nicki Minaj & More
description:
Today on The Breakfast Club, we opened the phone lines to hear what our listeners had to say about Boosie's comments on social media ruining relationships. Also, after going over the beef between Nicki and Latto in Angela's "Rumor Report", they lightened up the discussion with a "Freaky Friday" topic about masturbation, based off Jamaican artist Spice's comments on it from Angela Yee "Lip Service" pocast.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
